Ladysmith residents went on a rampage in the town overnight. Six cars at the Social Development Department were torched. This comes amid protests calling for the removal of mayor Vincent Madlala. Ladysmith residents blocked roads on Thursday demanding the removal of mayor Vincent Madlala. Mabopane train station will remain closed while the railway lines between the station and Pretoria are being repaired. Minister of Transport Fikile Mbalula presented the Passenger Rail Agency's plan to renovate the line, which  is currently only operating at 16 percent capacity.